nd pipes into smart networks offering complete network visibility application control and subscriber management in  the company reported  million in revenue contents  history  acquisitions  products  controversy  references  external links historyedit allot communications was founded in  by michael shurman and yigal jacoby who served as chief executive and chairman until  jacoby previously founded armon networking a manufacturer of rmonbased network management solutions which was sold to bay networks for  million in  in november  deloitte  touche named allot the fourth fastestgrowing company on its israel technology fast  list citing the companys revenue growth of nearly  in a years time by  allot raised  million in several rounds of funding from several venture capital funds including genesis partners gemini walden israel jafco investment bancboston capital jerusalem venture partners and tamar technology ventures in  rami hadar was appointed president and ceo in november  allot became a publicly traded company on the nasdaq global market under the ticker symbol allt the ipo raised  million in november  allots dual listing on the tel aviv stock exchange was approved allot partnered with openet in january  to optimize monetization of mobile broadband networks allot was featured on the deloitte fast  list in  for a  growth between  and  allot joined the hp opennfv partner program in july  allowing it to expand its traffic detection function and security services onto the hp opennfv platform nokia networks partnered with allot communications in january  to enhance visibility control and security for swisscom later that year allot partnered with intel security to release mcafee unified security powered by allot which focused on endtoend security capabilities acquisitionsedit in september  allot acquired netreality a provider of network application priority switches naps in order to enhance its quality of service qos and bandwidth management solutions allot acquired esphion a new zealand–based developer of network protection solutions for carriers and internet service providers in january  the acquisition expanded allots mitigation of security threats with the addition of isolation and remedy of infected subscribers and distributed denial of service ddos attack prevention in may  allot acquired ortiva wireless a san diegobased developer of video traffic optimization equipment allot acquired oversi networks a provider of richmedia caching and content delivery solutions for internet video and peertopeer pp traffic in july  in march  allot acquired global it security company optenet which expanded the companys securityasaservice offerings productsedit allot provides intelligent ip service optimization solutions for dsl wireless broadband carriers service providers and enterprises allots portfolio of hardware platforms and software applications employs dpi to turn broadband pipes into smart networks so that valueadded internet services can be rapidly deployed allot sgsigma released in  was designed to increase subscriber quality of experience qoe with the ability to generate additional revenue streams in  allot released the allot service gateway tera as a unified framework for physical and virtual deployment across access networks in december  allot unveiled allot cloud access optimization designed for enterprises and cloud managed service providers which has three levels of coverage and can be used with office  and adds visibility control and security to applications allot smartengage designed to enhance company engagement with subscribers was launched in february  smartengage uses allot service gateways traffic awareness feature to suggest content based on browsing activity in may  vodafone germany announced its deployment of allot websafe personal a networkbased securityasaservice offering designed for mobile users as well as small and medium business clients which includes antimalware and parental control options later that same year allot released the allot service gatewayvirtual edition allot sgve the original service gateway was introduced in  to improve efficiency and monetization options for companies the new framework integrates the gateway framework with a virtual network to remove physical hardware constraints in february  allot released the allot service gateway  expanding its capabilities to include enterprises data centers and service providers in june  belgian cable company announced that it began using allot service gateway tera and allot serviceprotector for network traffic analysis along with allots cmts to manage congestion and qos assurance controversyedit in  reports alleged that allot had been illegally selling equipment to iran however in january  allot was cleared by the ministry of defense of any wrongdoing also in  allot settled a classaction lawsuit regarding securities fraud involving its stock whereby it agreed to pay  million usd referencesedit  a b c allot communications investors presentation pdf allot communications march  retrieved  december    a b elgin ben  december  israel didn’t know hightech gear was sent to iran bloomberg businessweek   a b grigonis richard march   allot communications sigma service gateway tmcnetcom   a b c dar zuri  allot communications wraps up  million financing round the marker archived from the original on  cs maint bot originalurl status unknown link  bay networks acquires armon networking israel business today march     krawitz avi november   allot raises m in nasdaq listing the jerusalem post   form k securities and exchange commission retrieved december     allot openet teamup for policy management openet january   retrieved december     technology fast israel  pdf deloitte retrieved december     paula bernier july   allot brings virtual traffic detection to hp opennfv nfv zone retrieved december     allot communications offers security for hp opennfv cloud pipeline july   retrieved december     gina narcisi january   wheeling an